Téléchargement de boost : 


https://waqarrashid33.blogspot.com/2017/12/installing-boost-166-in-ubuntu-1604.html



Compilation for the server :  

g++ serverBoost.cpp -std=gnu++11 -lboost_system -lboost_thread -lboost_timer -pthread -o server

Compilatoin for the client :    

g++ clientBoost.cpp -std=gnu++11 -lboost_system -lboost_thread -lboost_timer -pthread -o client
